---
import "../../styles/global.css";
/* src/components/StatementGuide.astro */
---

<div
  class="not-content my-8 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-md"
>
  <div
    class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-6 py-5"
  >
    <div
      class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl shadow"
    >
      üìù
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-1">
      <h3 class="m-0 text-lg font-bold text-rose-800">
        Statement of Impact Guide
      </h3>
      <p class="m-0 text-sm text-rose-800">
        Your opportunity to explain how the offence has affected your life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5">
    <div
      class="border-b border-gray-100 p-6 md:col-span-3 md:border-b-0 md:border-r"
    >
      <strong class="text-gray-900">What to include:</strong>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-none space-y-3 p-0">
        <li class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <span class="min-w-[80px] font-bold text-rose-800">Physical:</span> Injuries,
          pain, scarring, treatment needed.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <span class="min-w-[80px] font-bold text-rose-800">Emotional:</span> Fear,
          anxiety, sleep issues, trauma.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <span class="min-w-[80px] font-bold text-rose-800">Social:</span> Impact
          on relationships, safety, or social life.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <span class="min-w-[80px] font-bold text-rose-800">Financial:</span> Lost
          wages, medical costs, damaged items.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 bg-gray-50 p-6 text-center md:col-span-2"
    >
      <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600">
        There is no strict format. You can use dot points, a letter, or a
        statutory declaration.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/Statement_of_Impact.pdf"
        class="flex w-full max-w-xs items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-rose-800 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white no-underline transition hover:bg-rose-900"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <span class="text-lg leading-none"></span> Download Official Guide
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
